05 OPTIMIZE YOUR GPS SETTINGS

   At any moment you can choose to switch from one GPS formula to another,
   in order to optimize your business depending on your needs.

06 WATCH YOUR BUSINESS AND INCOME GROW

   GPS is designed to put your business potentially on auto-pilot,
   providing marketing novices and experts, with a powerful and unique
   cash-flow generating asset.

